
{ Run levels

  • 0: halt
  • 1: Single user mode
  • 2: Multi user, without networking
  • 3: Full multi user mode
  • 4: user definable
  • 5: Full multi user with → Linux/X/display-manager[display manager]
  • 6: reboot.

  The runlevels are controlled via the → Linux/fhs/etc/inittab file.

}

sa:

  → Linux/init/systemd
